# Secondary button color token

When user says "secondary button color", use `Color("ButtonSecondaryBgColor")` from the asset catalog.
- Light mode: stone-300 (#D6D3D1)
- Dark mode: stone-800 (#292524)

**Why:** User defined this as the standard secondary/dismiss button background, distinct from the primary accent-colored action button.

**How to apply:** Any dismiss/cancel/secondary action button should use this background color with `PrimaryTextColor` foreground, capsule shape, same padding as primary buttons.
